About Us

Zambia's Trusted
Construction Partner

Jastallers Construction Limited is a premier construction and renovation company based in Lusaka, Zambia. We bring skill, craftsmanship, and dedication to every project — from simple paint jobs to full building extensions and commercial fit-outs.

Our experienced team handles everything from concept to completion, ensuring quality workmanship that stands the test of time. Whether you need your office renovated, your home transformed, or a new structure built, we deliver results that exceed expectations.

Located off Manchinchi Road, Woodfield, Lusaka — serving clients across Zambia with professional construction services at competitive rates.
